    "TitleKey": "headhunters_bombingrun_E_title_001",
    "Description": "Some competition has taken root at ~mission(Location|Address) and they've really been gumming up the works for our operations in the area.\n\nNow part of me sees some potential in the upstarts so I'm hoping to bring them into fold, but at the same time, I can't really afford to have them flying around causing trouble.\n\nInstead, I want you to go and blow up their fuel tanks. That should keep them grounded long enough for me to talk some sense into their thick heads.\n\n-Stows out",
